{"tid":1673212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯：學生或者青年人知唔知乜嘢叫「DLLM」吖","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T04:58:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9da28500b6141668de10a7e1b85ed60cb8a681fa","tid":1673212,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n唔止大鬧甲甴，何君堯講講下仲反問，「學生或者青年人知唔知乜嘢叫DLLM(粗口拼音)吖」，但當時未有任何人要求收回言論。其後鄭松泰喺發言時，就鬧爆立法會主席梁君彥聽到DLLM竟然冇反應，質疑梁係唔知背後個意思，接受議會以下三流方式去描述人同事，定係接受用英文縮寫去替代廣東話粗口。鬧完梁君彥，鄭松泰仲鬧何君堯嘅言論係下三流、反人類同反人道，話冇可能確認中大學生係示威者，唔應該用曱甴去稱呼人。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191024/bkn-20191024184423664-1024_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR0ja2h-4ElzY_8Ydgl9soWzd9Y89GKdHyS6OvbuHTFy_QV-YCqkX-PVNx8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191024%2Fbkn-20191024184423664-1024_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ja2h-4ElzY_8Ydgl9soWzd9Y89GKdHyS6OvbuHTFy_QV-YCqkX-PVNx8&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNtOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=1b998171\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191024/bkn-20191024184423664-1024_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR0ja2h-4ElzY_8Ydgl9soWzd9Y89GKdHyS6OvbuHTFy_QV-YCqkX-PVNx8</a>"},{"pid":"c7ee9378e79e6444368ac4a3a4441d7159c75aec","tid":1673212,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guewjRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguewjRY.jpg&h=ac95176a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"446a8abbc5b855f1c5b830ff557bfc92f86647c1","tid":1673212,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953fad9c08974335554d769af8c804a058f3a0d5","tid":1673212,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:47:12.000Z","msg":"DLLM"},{"pid":"10f8a69f7a2b46